## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all aspects of the complex relationship between inflation and the housing market. The data and insights are subject to change as new economic conditions and policies emerge. Additionally, the report does not account for regional variations in the housing market, which can significantly influence the impact of inflation on housing prices and affordability.